1
00:00:18,582 --> 00:00:21,420
♪Wearing peach blossom makeup,
I boil tea over the stove♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,780
♪With a pure heart,
I embroider the brocade of time♪

3
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,380
♪On the short paper,
affection flows in the silent moonlight♪

4
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:34,940
♪I only wish that by my side,
is my love♪

5
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Cool autumn wind blowing,
I gaze far leaning against the railing♪

6
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:44,460
♪Sunset glow over the green hill,
in formation wild geese are flying♪

7
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:50,020
♪Covering a thousand miles on horseback,
for whom is he longing♪

8
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:53,620
♪He returned home in dreams♪

9
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:58,220
♪I will never forget
that you held my hands♪

10
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:03,020
♪In your warm palms
and we braved winds and waves♪

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Unexpectedly, after we traveled so far
and turned Grey-haired♪

12
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:12,260
♪I am still by your side♪

13
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:16,820
♪Hearts burning,
we look into each other's eyes♪

14
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,500
♪Feelings overflowing,
they don't need to be hided♪

15
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:26,500
♪No matter how time passes
and life changes♪

16
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:31,060
♪Together, we will grow old♪

17
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:36,331
=The Sword and the Brocade=

18
00:01:37,119 --> 00:01:39,250
=Episode 15=

19
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,838
(Xuanya Painting and Calligraphy)

20
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,400
Take care.

21
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,920
Madam.

22
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,920
These are too expensive.

23
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,640
They are.

24
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,400
But as long as it can make Concubine Qiao

25
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,640
change her mind,

26
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,520
it will be worth it.

27
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,800
I hope that your efforts

28
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,760
won't be wasted.

29
00:02:10,135 --> 00:02:12,448
(Xuanya Painting and Calligraphy)

30
00:02:12,449 --> 00:02:13,807
(Xiangfu Vinegar Shop)

31
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,360
Isn't that Mrs. Zhang?

32
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,120
Why is she here?

33
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,680
(Vinegar)

34
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:36,640
(Rice Vinegar)

35
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,693
(Vinegar)

36
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,800
Hurry up.

37
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,600
Hurry.

38
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:01,964
(Vinegar)

39
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:07,960
Let's go.

40
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,400
Are you serious?

41
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,480
I'm very sure.

42
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,880
I personally saw it.

43
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,240
No wonder.

44
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,920
I knew it.

45
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,760
Why did she buy so much rice vinegar?

46
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,040
I guessed it right indeed.

47
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,560
If you pour enough rice vinegar

48
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,200
into the water used to wash rice,

49
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,440
it will remove the moldy smell
in the water.

50
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,480
Merchants

51
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,200
pull this trick too many times.

52
00:03:47,399 --> 00:03:48,280
Those rice

53
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,240
was too moldy already.

54
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,200
Back home,

55
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,040
we won't even use them

56
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,320
to feed the pigs.

57
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,000
Rice vinegar

58
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,120
can remove the moldy smell of rice,

59
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,160
but it can't eliminate its toxicity.

60
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:01,760
People will die if they eat it.

61
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,680
Since it's that serious,

62
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:04,760
Mrs. Zhang

63
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,720
is too bold.

64
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,320
Mrs. Zhang

65
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,600
isn't bold enough.

66
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,600
Madam.

67
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,800
I'm afraid we can't
disclose this matter.

68
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,440
After this, this involves His Lordship.

69
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,200
His Lordship is still young.

70
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,320
He'll surely get another legal wife
in the future.

71
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,440
Should we let Concubine Qiao
ascend to position

72
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,040
making things difficult for you,

73
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,200
or let the wives help each other

74
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,440
like a tripartite balance of forces?

75
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,560
Which one do you think

76
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:39,480
would benefit the Wen family

77
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,720
and you more?

78
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,240
There's an opportunity
for the Wen family

79
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,520
to overturn the situation now.

80
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,680
I must think about this carefully.

81
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,360
How strange.

82
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,600
Qiuhong.

83
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,200
Nanny Tao.

84
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,840
What's the matter?

85
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,080
I went to the kitchen just now

86
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,640
to get some porridge for Concubine Wen.

87
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,280
Who knew that the servant in the kitchen

88
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,400
ran out

89
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,800
and even took the porridge away.

90
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,640
She said that she got it mixed up,

91
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,440
and it will be bad if we'll get
a stomachache after eating it.

92
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,280
Perhaps something dirty

93
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,840
got mixed in there.

94
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,800
Qiuhong.

95
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,720
You said something

96
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,960
got mixed up?

97
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:36,960
Yes.

98
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,080
What's the matter, Nanny Tao?

99
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,280
Nothing,

100
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,240
It's nothing.

101
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,160
Moldy rice?

102
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,440
Nanny Tao.

103
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,680
You're so flustered.

104
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,960
Where are you going?

105
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,920
I... I'm fine.

106
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,080
Oh, right.

107
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,000
You... Do what you have to do.

108
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,000
Do what you have to do.

109
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,720
Do what I have to do?

110
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,760
She's not usually this way.

111
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,560
This is bad.

112
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,960
What happened?

113
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,200
Don't be anxious, Madam.

114
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,560
It's done.

115
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,560
Really?

116
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,680
This trick

117
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:41,720
is amazing.

118
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,480
Next,

119
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,120
we just need to see what will happen.

120
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,120
Oh, right.

121
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,960
I'm just not sure what Her Ladyship

122
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,000
will do.

123
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,560
Her Ladyship has gotten ahold

124
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,000
of such a big mistake.

125
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,640
If she has the boldness

126
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,160
of the late Her Ladyship back then,

127
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,760
she'll surely use this opportunity

128
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,120
to defeat Concubine Qiao

129
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,840
and get back the authority to manage
household affairs.

130
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,640
Before,

131
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:04,440
the late Her Ladyship was nice
to the Wen family.

132
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,360
Since Her Ladyship is her younger sister,

133
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,200
she'll surely be easy to get along with
in the future.

134
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,920
So the Wen family can change
our fortunes

135
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,360
very soon.

136
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,600
Nanny Tao.

137
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,120
You served Yuanniang

138
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,360
for a long time.

139
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,920
Do you know that the punishment

140
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,120
for making a false charge against
a master

141
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,480
isn't just flogging?

142
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,400
Your Ladyship, don't worry.

143
00:08:37,680 --> 00:08:39,000
If I didn't have any evidence,

144
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,840
how would I dare

145
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,280
make such groundless accusation?

146
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:42,640
By the way, Your Ladyship,

147
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,800
you didn't see

148
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,960
those bags of rice.

149
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,720
Only a thin layer

150
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,680
of good rice is on top of them.

151
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:49,400
The rest are all moldy.

152
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,480
It's obvious that someone
tampered with them.

153
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,800
I think

154
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,320
Concubine Qiao

155
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,360
has long planned

156
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,040
to make some money on the rice

157
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,680
for the porridge.

158
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,960
Even if she doesn't get enough money
from her usual portion,

159
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,160
the Qiao family is so rich.

160
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,560
She wouldn't lack money.

161
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,280
Why would she do this?

162
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,520
Your Ladyship, you're thinking
too highly of her.

163
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,440
Who isn't tempted

164
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,400
by money?

165
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,800
Yes, the Qiao family is rich indeed.

166
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,000
But the Qiao family

167
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,000
isn't just

168
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,880
hers alone.

169
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:24,680
Are you sure what you saw
was moldy rice?

170
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,000
Did you see it clearly?

171
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,400
I did.

172
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,480
If... If I'm speaking nonsense,

173
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,880
I'll... I'll be struck

174
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,960
by lightning.

175
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:37,920
By the way, I also heard

176
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,080
that inside the soup kitchen,

177
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,800
there are a lot of grain supplies.

178
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,720
Who else knows about this?

179
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,240
It seems like

180
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,280
aside from Mrs. Zhang's staff,

181
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:48,080
I'm the only one who knows about this.

182
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,120
How did you find out then?

183
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,800
Concubine Wen's maid Qiuhong

184
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,880
said that she got the wrong porridge.

185
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,800
So what if she did?

186
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,800
So I thought

187
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:00,040
the problem must be with the rice.

188
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,840
Then I went to the warehouse to check.

189
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,040
By the way,

190
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,400
on my way back,

191
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,920
I even met Mrs. Zhang's maid,

192
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,920
Xialing.

193
00:10:09,319 --> 00:10:10,640
This is a major matter.

194
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,880
Don't disclose this to anyone.

195
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:14,160
Come with me to the warehouse.

196
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,000
Mrs. Zhang.

197
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,120
Mrs. Zhang.

198
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,280
Bad news.

199
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,320
Earlier,

200
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,240
I met Nanny Tao,

201
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:28,920
who came very flustered

202
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,320
from the direction of the warehouse.

203
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,840
I went inside to take a look.

204
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,480
Who would have thought
that the door to the warehouse

205
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,480
was open?

206
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,000
I think

207
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,520
she must already know.

208
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,640
Go... Go back now

209
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,920
and lock the door of the warehouse.

210
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,560
No one can go inside again.

211
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,840
-Go, hurry.
-All right.

212
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,640
Wait.

213
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,800
Go, open the door of the warehouse.

214
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,320
The key is with Mrs. Zhang.

215
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,440
Where's Mrs. Zhang?

216
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,320
I don't know.

217
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:11,520
Your Ladyship.

218
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,880
Let's find someone
to break the door open.

219
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,760
Your Ladyship.

220
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:20,880
Your Ladyship.

221
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,320
Your Ladyship, where are you going?

222
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,440
The soup kitchen

223
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,480
is full of moldy rice now.

224
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,680
If they continue investigating...

225
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,080
You're so bold.

226
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,080
How dare you use moldy rice
to make porridge?

227
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,080
Don't you know

228
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,080
how important this is to Great Madam?

229
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,880
If you need money, just tell me.

230
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,200
Why did you tamper
with the relief grains?

231
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:44,320
Madam... Madam, I am wrong.

232
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,880
It's all my son's fault.

233
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,160
He owes a huge debt.

234
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,800
They'll kill him.

235
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,640
How would I dare to tell you about this?

236
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,320
How long have you been using moldy rice?

237
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,440
Two days.

238
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,560
Just two days.

239
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:58,840
I waited for Great Madam

240
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,080
to light the incense at the temple

241
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,320
before I dared to use it.

242
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:02,080
I originally thought

243
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,120
about buying some moldy rice
to earn some money

244
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,160
and stop after I earn enough.

245
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,680
Who would have thought...

246
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,040
Who would have thought
that someone would find out?

247
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:10,920
Don't you know

248
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,360
that people will die from eating
moldy rice?

249
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,640
If something really happens,

250
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,080
and the government blames us for it,

251
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:19,440
the entire Xu family
will be dragged down.

252
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:20,920
His Lordship...

253
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,120
What will His Lordship think of me?

254
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,040
Madam.

255
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,640
Madam, I was wrong.

256
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,960
I dragged you down.

257
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,560
I'll go to His Lordship now.

258
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,920
I'll seek punishment from His Lordship
and Great Madam.

259
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,640
I'll tell them that it's all my fault,

260
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:36,880
it has nothing to do with you.

261
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:37,920
No.

262
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,440
You're working for me.

263
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:41,360
I can't evade the responsibility
for this no matter what.

264
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,160
Xiuyuan.

265
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:45,120
Let's go and borrow rice
from the Qiao family immediately.

266
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,760
We just need to replace the rice

267
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,480
before Luo Shiyi

268
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,760
finds out.

269
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,680
Then we can still redeem the situation.

270
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,200
This matter cannot be delayed.

271
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,840
Let's go to
the soup kitchen immediately.

272
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,880
Thank you, Madam.

273
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:02,240
Here, take it.

274
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,520
Here, this is yours.

275
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,480
Thank you.

276
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,480
Line up properly.

277
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,520
Thank you.

278
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,600
Your Ladyship.

279
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,880
Your Ladyship.

280
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,560
If you don't guard the warehouse,

281
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,600
if they remove

282
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,840
the moldy rice,

