their moldy rice any longer.

857
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:41,200
I can't believe Xu Lingyi's wife

858
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,880
lasts this long.

859
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:44,880
I've belittled her.

860
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,880
Tell them to watch
the soup kitchen closely.

861
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:48,840
Don't let them get any chance

862
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,080
to remove the moldy rice.

863
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,040
Yes.

864
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,120
If the Ou family can't
cause us trouble today,

865
00:34:58,560 --> 00:35:00,320
they'll surely find another opportunity.

866
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,240
However,

867
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,400
our rice supply now

868
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:05,000
is only enough for a couple of days.

869
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,000
We must find

870
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,320
enough new rice.

871
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:09,680
But the Ou family

872
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,400
just wants everyone to know
about the moldy rice.

873
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,680
We can just move

874
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,120
the moldy rice away secretly.

875
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,080
They were even watching

876
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:16,640
the Qiao family's horse carriage
that was supposed to bring rice.

877
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,200
And they spent so much money

878
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,680
to buy all the rice in the city.

879
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,640
How can they let us

880
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:22,280
move the moldy rice away so smoothly?

881
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:25,400
If we really moved the moldy rice,

882
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:26,360
perhaps

883
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:27,960
they'd catch us in the act.

884
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:32,080
I wonder

885
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,640
what happened with Amber.

886
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,800
Alms.

887
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,080
You are so kind.

888
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:42,880
Give us some food.

889
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:45,840
It's mine.

890
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,207
(Wine)

891
00:35:47,280 --> 00:35:47,760
Don't take what's mine.

892
00:35:47,959 --> 00:35:48,360
Give it to me.

893
00:35:48,479 --> 00:35:48,999
Give it to me.

894
00:35:49,876 --> 00:35:51,583
(Vinegar)

895
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:52,720
Move.

896
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:55,959
Give it to me.

897
00:35:57,640 --> 00:35:58,200
Give it to me.

898
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:01,600
Stop taking it away.

899
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:03,760
Stop taking it away.

900
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,200
Give me some food.

901
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:07,680
After just a few years,

902
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,399
the capital changed so much.

903
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:10,760
There are so many refugees.

904
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:13,680
The flooding disaster this time

905
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:15,080
must be serious.

906
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:18,640
Young Master, should we go
to the shop first?

907
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:20,439
There's no rush.

908
00:36:22,959 --> 00:36:24,280
Alms.

909
00:36:25,040 --> 00:36:25,880
Alms.

910
00:36:26,399 --> 00:36:27,439
Please.

911
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:28,560
I really need it urgently.

912
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:30,479
My master really needs it.

913
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:32,360
(Fengping Grains)
I told you many times.

914
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,880
No matter how much
you're willing to pay,

915
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:35,400
we won't sell our rice to you.

916
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:36,480
Be nice.

917
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,600
Let me in.

918
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,080
I really need it urgently.

919
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:39,960
Can you let me in?

920
00:36:40,160 --> 00:36:40,920
Are you done yet?

921
00:36:57,080 --> 00:36:57,960
Young lady, are you all right?

922
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:00,840
I'm fine.

923
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:02,080
Thank you, sir.

924
00:37:04,516 --> 00:37:06,243
(Fengping Grains)

925
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:09,240
Why do you need to buy rice
so urgently?

926
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,160
My master

927
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:11,360
needs rice for disaster relief.

928
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,080
But the keeper

929
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:12,720
won't sell me rice

930
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:14,120
no matter what.

931
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:15,480
Most likely,

932
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,160
the keeper is afraid
that you're buying rice

933
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:19,200
to sell them at a high price
and harm the citizens.

934
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,080
That's why he's not willing
to sell them to you.

935
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,160
Why would we do that?

936
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,560
My master is...

937
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:26,720
My master

938
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:27,520
won't do

939
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:28,960
such a terrible thing.

940
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:31,960
Since they're willing to buy rice
at a high price,

941
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,880
they're surely not people
who will pull tricks.

942
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:36,080
Come with me inside.

943
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:37,160
But...

944
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:45,440
(Grains)

945
00:37:49,704 --> 00:37:51,604
(Rice)

946
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:52,600
Young lady.

947
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:53,760
You think I really won't
get physical with you,

948
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:54,560
do you?

949
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:55,400
Sir.

950
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:57,640
Sell this young lady

951
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,040
the rice that she wants.

952
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,560
Follow the market price.

953
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:02,840
You're so arrogant.

954
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:03,480
Don't you see

955
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:04,440
what kind of place this is?

956
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:06,320
Can you act so impetuously here?

957
00:38:13,519 --> 00:38:15,120
(Ou)

958
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:25,520
Sir, you...

959
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,720
Young lady.

960
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:28,800
How much rice do you want?

961
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,560
We'll sell them at the market price.

962
00:38:30,720 --> 00:38:31,440
Really?

963
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:33,760
Thank you, sir.

964
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:35,760
Thank you, sir.

965
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,200
Dongqing.

966
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:52,000
Look, we're out of rice.

967
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:53,200
Right.

968
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:54,000
What should we do?

969
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:55,480
Your Ladyship.

970
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:57,680
Our good rice is all used up.

971
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:59,000
Only moldy rice is left.

972
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,520
If we can't give out more porridge,

973
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:02,320
we can only shut down the soup kitchen.

974
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:04,360
The Wang family's soup kitchen

975
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:05,480
might still have some extra rice.

976
00:39:05,680 --> 00:39:06,040
What if

977
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:06,840
we lead the refugees

978
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:07,920
over there first?

979
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:08,920
Perhaps we can control

980
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:10,080
the chaotic situation.

981
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:11,080
No.

982
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,680
All the Marquis in the capital

983
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,040
are providing disaster relief according
to His Majesty's imperial edict.

984
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,640
Each family is responsible
for one soup kitchen.

985
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,560
Soldiers are guarding between each area.

986
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,600
If chaos occurs

987
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,720
and they investigate it,

988
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:21,920
I'm afraid we won't be able

989
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:23,520
to hide the moldy rice.

990
00:39:26,640 --> 00:39:28,360
When will you give out porridge?

991
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:29,400
Give them out.

992
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:29,840
Is there rice?

993
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:32,360
Everyone, quiet down.

994
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,000
Let me tell you, there's no more rice.

995
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:35,680
There's no rice.

996
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:36,920
Be kind.

997
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:39,360
Give the children some porridge.

998
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:41,960
They're starving.

999
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,880
We want porridge.

1000
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,000
There is so much rice.

1001
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:50,240
Why won't you cook them?

1002
00:39:50,480 --> 00:39:50,840
Right.

1003
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:51,680
There is so much rice.

1004
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:53,040
Why won't you cook them?

1005
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:58,040
Your Ladyship.

1006
00:39:58,240 --> 00:39:58,960
Once people get hungry,

1007
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,040
they're capable of doing anything.

1008
00:40:00,240 --> 00:40:01,080
Based on the situation outside,

1009
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:02,080
I'm afraid they'll cause trouble.

1010
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:02,760
At a time like this,

1011
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:03,920
your safety is the priority.

1012
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:05,600
Go back to the mansion
and avoid them first.

1013
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,560
No.

1014
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:07,640
In times like these,

1015
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,080
I can't leave all the more.

1016
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,360
Your Ladyship.

1017
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,280
We haven't eaten yet.

1018
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:29,640
We're all waiting.

1019
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,040
I'm apologizing

1020
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:35,800
to everyone.

1021
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:38,080
We didn't watch the relief grains well,

1022
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:39,560
and rats got to them.

1023
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,600
We're afraid that you'll get sick
if you eat them.

1024
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,840
I've already sent people
to get new rice.

1025
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:46,280
Please be patient and wait for a while.

1026
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:47,680
How can we wait?

1027
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,320
Right.

1028
00:40:49,520 --> 00:40:51,360
The children can't wait.

1029
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,160
What should we do?

1030
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:55,360
So what if the rats got to them?

1031
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:55,880
Right, Madam Xu.

1032
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:56,640
We're farmers,

1033
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:57,280
we're not that particular.

1034
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,640
-I want to eat.
-Right.

1035
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,640
You can just feed the children first.

1036
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,160
Yes, feed the children first.

1037
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:04,280
Please be patient.

1038
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,280
No.

1039
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:06,440
I'll stay here

1040
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:07,800
and wait together with you all.

1041
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:09,400
If new rice doesn't arrive,

1042
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:11,080
you can come to me.

1043
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,880
If it doesn't arrive,

1044
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,280
we'll starve to death then.

1045
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,120
Everyone!

1046
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:16,800
Everyone!

1047
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,120
Let me say something!

1048
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,360
Since Madam Xu

1049
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:20,920
already said that,

1050
00:41:21,160 --> 00:41:22,280
so what if we wait

1051
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:23,080
just a bit longer?

1052
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:23,960
Let's wait.

1053
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,960
-Yes.
-Right.

1054
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:35,120
Master Lixing, I don't understand.

1055
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:36,000
Why don't we let

1056
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:36,720
the people we've arranged

1057
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:38,080
charge into the soup kitchen directly

1058
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:39,320
and bring the moldy rice out?

1059
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,520
Then we'll have the evidence too.

1060
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,720
The Xu family won't be able
to deny it any longer.

1061
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:45,360
I can't incite the refugees
to go on a riot.

1062
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:46,520
Even if our people

1063
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:48,240
take the moldy rice out,

1064
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:49,960
it's unavoidable for them
to leave a trace.

1065
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,520
Perhaps

1066
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:53,360
Xu Lingyi will even make countercharges
against us,

1067
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:54,520
and say

1068
00:41:55,240 --> 00:41:57,920
that we've exchanged the rice
to frame him.

1069
00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,360
You're right.

1070
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:01,320
I'm too impatient.

1071
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:04,120
We've been fighting with the Xu family
for so many years.

1072
00:42:04,360 --> 00:42:06,440
We can wait a bit longer.

1073
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:07,920
Yes.

1074
00:42:11,720 --> 00:42:13,520
Sir, it's up ahead.

1075
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,240
Hurry.

1076
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:23,680
Wait.

1077
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,960
Sir, let's go another way.

1078
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,320
We've been waiting for so long.

1079
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:38,680
When exactly will you

1080
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:39,360
give out porridge?

1081
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,760
-Right.
-When will you give out porridge?

1082
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,080
Everyone, listen to me.

1083
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:44,960
Stop listening to her nonsense.

1084
00:42:45,160 --> 00:42:46,560
No new rice will arrive.

1085
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:47,440
I heard

1086
00:42:47,640 --> 00:42:48,960
that they're keeping the rice

1087
00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:50,960
to sell them at a high price.

1088
00:42:51,240 --> 00:42:52,760
How can these rich people

1089
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,640
really care about us?

1090
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:55,480
That's nonsense.

1091
00:42:55,720 --> 00:42:56,360
Right.

1092
00:42:57,160 --> 00:42:57,720
Liars.

1093
00:42:57,720 --> 00:42:59,560
They're liars.

1094
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:00,440
Your Ladyship.

1095
00:43:01,200 --> 00:43:03,240
Don't listen to gossip.

1096
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:05,680
I guarantee on behalf of the Xu family

1097
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:06,880
that within the disaster period,

1098
00:43:07,080 --> 00:43:07,800
every one of you

1099
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:08,960
will have food to eat.

1100
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:10,400
Where's the food?

1101
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:12,320
Don't listen to her lies.

1102
00:43:12,680 --> 00:43:14,320
Let's fill our stomachs first.

1103
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:16,040
Let's go inside to get some rice!

1104
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,360
Let's go!

1105
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:21,600
Everyone, calm down.

1106
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:22,920
Everyone, calm down.

1107
00:43:23,120 --> 00:43:23,920
Move!

1108
00:43:26,240 --> 00:43:27,640
Your Ladyship!

1109
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:35,680
Don't push.

1110
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:36,760
Your Ladyship.

1111
00:43:43,560 --> 00:43:45,240
Don't take them!

1112
00:43:47,120 --> 00:43:47,760
Move.

1113
00:43:48,120 --> 00:43:49,560
You can't take them!

1114
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:54,960
Don't push each other.

1115
00:43:55,200 --> 00:43:56,880
-Give it to me.
-Go away.

1116
00:43:56,880 --> 00:43:57,573
(Disaster Relief)

1117
00:43:58,160 --> 00:43:58,880
Let go!

1118
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:19,240
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

1119
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:22,640
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

1120
00:44:23,960 --> 00:44:30,520
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

1121
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:33,000
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

1122
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:37,600
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

1123
00:44:38,040 --> 00:44:44,200
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

1124
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:47,160
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

1125
00:44:48,080 --> 00:44:50,640
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

1126
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:58,680
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

1127
00:44:59,080 --> 00:45:01,280
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

1128
00:45:02,280 --> 00:45:05,720
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

1129
00:45:06,240 --> 00:45:12,000
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

1130
00:45:12,840 --> 00:45:19,720
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

1131
00:45:20,080 --> 00:45:26,720
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

1132
00:45:27,120 --> 00:45:30,440
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

1133
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:33,840
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

1134
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:41,040
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

1135
00:45:41,040 --> 00:45:47,960
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

